<hw>hazelwood</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A reddish-brown wood and lumber
from the heartwood of the sweet gum tree.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> sweet gum, satin walnut, red gum.</syn>⟦br⟧
